Interface ElementAccess<E>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ElementAccessFunction<E,I,O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AutomaticType, CollectorType, ConstraintType, CounterType, GetElement, GetElement.GetField, GetElement.GetListElement, GetElement.GetMapValue, GetElement.GetRelation, GetElement.GetRelationValue, GetElement.ReadField, ListenerType, ListType, MapType, RelationType, SetType, TimerType

    public interface ElementAccess<E>
    An interface for objects that implement access to certain elements of other objects. The descriptor of the accessed elements can be queried with the getElementDescriptor() method.
